 introduced by the German naturalist Ludwig Reichenbach in 1850. There are four subspecies. Distribution and habitat It is found in Brazil, Colombia, French Guiana, Guyana, Panama, Suriname, and Venezuela. Its natural habitats are subtropical or tropical moist lowland forest and heavily degraded former forest. References", "shortSummary": "The yellow-green grosbeak (Caryothraustes canadensis) is a species of grosbeak in the family Cardinalidae. Taxonomy In 1760 the French zool…", "locations": ["哥伦比亚", "法屬圭亞那", "圭亚那", "巴拿马", "蘇利南", "委內瑞拉"], "lat": -10.0, "lng": -52.0, "imageUrl": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7e/Yellow-Green_Grosbeack.jpg/960px-Yellow-Green_Grosbeack.jpg", "kingdomId": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylumId": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "classId": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genusId": "taxonomy-genus-caryothraustes", "speciesId": "taxonomy-species-caryothraustes-canadensis", "taxonomyIds": {"kingdom": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylum": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "class": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genus": "taxonomy-genus-caryothraustes", "species": "taxonomy-species-caryothraustes-canadensis"}, "expandable": true, "x": 173.96, "y": -587.59, "z": -641.19}, {"id": "taxonomy-species-caryothraustes-canadensis", "name": "Yellow-green grosbeak", "latinName": "Caryothraustes canadensis", "type": "taxonomy", "taxonomyLevel": "species", "summary": "Yellow-green grosbeak（Caryothraustes canadensis）是图谱中的分类级分类节点，当前关联1种鸟类，如Yellow-green grosbeak。", "expandable": true, "memberCount": 1, "x": 173.96, "y": -587.59, "z": -655.04}], "links": [{"key": "bird-yellow-green-grosbeak-d3d2ef39__belongs_to_species__taxonomy-species-caryothraustes-canadensis", "source": "bird-yellow-green-grosbeak-d3d2ef39", "target": "taxonomy-species-caryothraustes-canadensis", "relation": "belongs_to_species", "label": "属于种", "evidence": "依据 birds.csv 中的种字段补充。"}, {"key": "taxonomy-species-caryothraustes-canadensis__belongs_to_genus__taxonomy-genus-caryothraustes", "sou